nhc_headline: ...RAMON WEAKENS... ...EXPECTED TO BECOME A REMNANT LOW LATER TODAY...
summary:
...RAMON WEAKENS... ...EXPECTED TO BECOME A REMNANT LOW LATER TODAY...
 As of 1:00 AM PST Sun Nov 26
 the center of Ramon was located near 14.4, -123.4
 with movement W at 5 mph.
 The minimum central pressure was 1005 mb
 with maximum sustained winds of about 40 mph.
